title: Bulldozers, aircraft used to fight fire near New Mexico city - The Associated Press
content: Bulldozers, aircraft used to fight fire near New Mexico city  The Associated PressView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Over 1,000 firefighters backed by bulldozers and aircraft battled the largest active wildfire in the U.S. on Saturday after strong winds pushed it across some containment lines and closer to a small city in northern New Mexico.
